lead_paragraph: In spurts, Elijah Stewart felt bone-tired. His voice was nearly gone, too. His mind wandered to last season's triple-overtime loss to Colorado, too.

headline.print_headline: Southern California Edges No. 7 Arizona 103-101 in 4 OTs
